&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;As your wellness concierge, I will be responsible for ensuring smooth communication between our teams, coordinating any necessary appointments, and providing updates on the progress regarding your program and care.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Please don&amp;#39;t hesitate to reach out to me with any questions or concerns you might have regarding your health...I&amp;#39;m here to help!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;I look forward to working with you and getting to know you better. If there is anything I can do to assist you, please do not hesitate to contact me.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
